rental.headline: Freshly Painted 2 Bedroom Sought After River Precinct-2 Balconies. Huge Lock Up Garage-Walk to all Parramatta Amenities
rental.description:
Spacious unit in fantastic location. Stroll to tranquil Parramatta River & all Parramatta city amenities. Huge open living area. Lounge & dining both opening to sunny balconies with leafy outlook. Large main bedroom with built-in robe. Modern kitchen. Separate bath & shower. Separate toilet. Internal laundry.lock up garage. Enjoy privacy & security on top floor. East to West facing. NEW FLOOR BOARDS AND FRESHLY PAINTED.
Quiet block featuring tennis court & swimming pool. Fantastic location. Stroll to Parramatta river foreshore for leisurely walks, festivals. Walk to vibrant Eat Street restaurants & cafes. 10 minutes' walk to Westfield Shopping, train station, RiverCat ferry terminal & picturesque Parramatta Park.
Please contact your Exclusive Agent AB Property Consultants on 0470602056/0402961515 for viewing and application form.
